title: Malinowski concedes to Mejia in Democratic House special primary in New Jersey
description: With the race still too close to call, former congressman Tom Malinowski conceded to challenger Analilia Mejia in a Democratic primary to replace the seat vacated by New Jersey Gov. Mikie Sherrill.
